executor_description: This will import your menu data for mapping or will syncronize your menu.  In order for your menu to syncronize, your point of sale integration must be set as the source of truth on the merchant.  Enabling Source of Truth  Go to the merchant dashboard under advanced and then open the pos settings and turn on Source of Truth.  Manual Mapping  Manual mapping is no longer the recommended way to syncronize menus. Manual mapping will still work for existing integrations as long as the source of truth is not set on the merchant.
